name: Moon Cult
description:
Men are sad and happy. 

They separate or meet again.

The moon is bright or dim and may wax or disappear.

Nothing has been perfect since ancient times.

So let's wish that man survived as long as he could!

Although we are miles apart, we will share the beauties she displays.
